\v 1 \w  When  |strong="834" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.2" \w* \w  the wall  |strong="2346" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.4" \w* \w  had been rebuilt  |strong="1129" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.3" \w* \w  and I had set the doors  |strong="1817" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.6" \w* \w  in place ,  |strong="5975" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.5" \w* \w  the gatekeepers ,  |strong="7778" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.8" \w* \w  singers ,  |strong="7891" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.9" \w* \w  and Levites  |strong="3881" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.10" \w* \w  were appointed .  |strong="6485" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.1.7" \w* \v 2 \w  Then I put my brother  |strong="251" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.4" \w* \w  Hanani  |strong="2607" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.3" \w* \w  in charge  |strong="6680" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.1" \w* \w  of  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.9" \w* \w  Jerusalem ,  |strong="3389" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.10" \w* \w  along with Hananiah  |strong="2608" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.6" \w* \w  the commander  |strong="8269" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.7" \w* \w  of the fortress ,  |strong="1002" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.8" \w* \w  because  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.11" \w* \w  he  |strong="1931" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.12" \w* \w  was a faithful  |strong="571" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.14" \w* \w  man  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.13" \w* \w  who feared  |strong="3372" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.15" \w* \w  God  |strong="430" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.17" \w* \w  more than most .  |strong="7227" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.2.18" \w* \v 3 \w  And I told  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.1" \w* \w  them ,  |srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.2" \w* \w  “ Do not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.3" \w* \w  open  |strong="6605" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.4" \w* \w  the gates  |strong="8179" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.5" \w* \w  of Jerusalem  |strong="3389" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.6" \w* \w  until  |strong="5704" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.7" \w* \w  the sun  |strong="8121" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.9" \w* \w  is hot .  |strong="2552" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.8" \w* \w  While  |strong="5704" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.10" \w* \w  the guards  |strong="1992" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.11" \w* \w  are on duty ,  |strong="5975" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.12" \w* \w  keep the doors  |strong="1817" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.14" \w* \w  shut  |strong="1479" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.13" \w* \w  and securely fastened .  |strong="270" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.15" \w* \w  And appoint  |strong="5975" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.16" \w* \w  the residents  |strong="3427" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.18" \w* \w  of Jerusalem  |strong="3389" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.19" \w* \w  as guards ,  |strong="4931" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.17" \w* \w  some  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.20" \w* \w  at their posts  |strong="4929" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.21" \w* \w  and some  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.22" \w* \w  at  |strong="5048" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.23" \w* \w  their own homes . ”  |strong="1004" srcloc="WLC:NEH.7.3.24" \w* 
